Date: Thu, 30 Apr 2026 02:29:55 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 23/43] PopUpSettingsConfig: Migrate Pop-Up View settings to
 SettingsProvider

Move Pop-Up View settings into SettingsProvider with backup and validation support so controller state comes from one persistent source. This replaces the older scattered storage path.

Change-Id: Iefa00f21d6f895dcaf2885f578517c77fe441aa4
